title: El Vegetariano
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Indian, International, Macrobiotic, Organic, Take-out, Venezuelan
description: This place sells organic and macrobiotic products, soy meat, palmitas, hemp oil, hygienic products and many more. You can eat at the counter downstairs or a table upstairs. Two small tofu shishkebabs cost 41 BsF, while empanadas are 6 BsF. They also serve versions of traditional Latin American food as well as hamburgers and more.
